      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "INTREPID EAGLE (6) has a strong record here with five wins and two placings from eight starts. Recorded a one length win (36.62) in a Grade 4/5 last time at this track. Makes strong appeal on best. ASHBY GNOCCHI (1) has a strong winning strike-rate over this track and trip with two wins and a placing from four tries. Scored by 4.5 lengths last time (36.46) in a Grade 4/5 over 630m at this track. Looks a key chance on best figures. GRAMERCY GARRY (7) is a talented dog who is a winner of 14 races and filled a minor placing latest when third at Richmond (35.72). Goes very well here at the trip finding the frame in each of seven starts. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Hard to beat again. ZIPPING HOPKINS (2) hasn't been far away, finishing in the money twice in a row including last time in a NG at Wentworth Park over 520m.",
